#Xenic Poltergeist + Flayer Husk (#1085) - PARKED, engine bug confirmed.
#Animating an ATTACHED living weapon (husk mv1 -> should be a 1/1 creature,
#unattaching; its 0/0 germ dies) instead kills the HUSK ITSELF: probe shows
#the husk in the graveyard and only the poltergeist left on the battlefield.
#Suspect: the equipment-attachment SBA destroys an equipment that became a
#creature rather than unattaching it (living weapon should survive on the
#battlefield). The poltergeist basic animation is pinned separately
#(xenic_poltergeist_i1085.txt, passing).
[INIT]
firstmain
[PLAYER1]
manapool:{1}
inplay:xenic poltergeist
hand:flayer husk
[PLAYER2]
[DO]
flayer husk
goto firstmain
goto firstmain
xenic poltergeist
flayer husk
goto firstmain
goto firstmain
goto firstmain
[ASSERT]
FIRSTMAIN
[PLAYER1]
inplay:xenic poltergeist,flayer husk
tappedinplay:1
[PLAYER2]
[END]
